{"tid":1745775,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"天琦有嘢同大家講","createTime":"2019-11-22T11:33:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T14:24:02.000Z","uid":73959,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"92955d357ebc8a4746bc1bfe4882538e3cd3a3cc","tid":1745775,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T11:33:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/WMfqjvB5l9E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FWMfqjvB5l9E&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRyljr7MFgrQ0V0XG6LyL0fmAc%3D&h=7833e0fa\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/WMfqjvB5l9E</a><br />\n<br />\n請花兩分鐘時間睇睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;但我只希望今日一個看似沒用的集會遊行，是會繼續影響更加多人。因為我明白我們不斷將手指指向上一代的人，為何香港今時今日變成這個樣子。我們的下一代將來也會用手指指向我們這一代人，質問我們今時今日做過什麼。有這樣的自覺，我們就知道再不是有用和沒用的問題，而是當下到底有什麼我們應該做而還沒做。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n我知道呢兩個星期發生咗好多事<br />\n就算人權法案過咗 <br />\n大家都開心唔起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n理大傷得重 分化風向撚不停進場 <br />\n導致大家意見分歧 唔能夠理性討論<br />\n<br />\n呢樣嘢係正常㗎 千其唔可以悲觀<br />\n一悲觀就等如認輸<br />\n去到樽頸位要突破就一定要諗新嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n與其唔開心<br />\n倒不如去brainstorm有咩要做而未做啦<br />\n記唔記得呀<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">不分和勇</span></strong></span>呀！<br />\n<br />\n和&gt;勇&gt;和&gt;勇<br />\n不停loop大家話好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb4584dbe60a406b52f272ce768ec75ab556d8c9","tid":1745775,"uid":121145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T11:34:04.000Z","msg":"P<br />\nU<br />\nS<br />\nH"},{"pid":"e11c19b9ddc5ee2aa6b54f26bed26a029859d814","tid":1745775,"uid":131766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T11:36:25.000Z","msg":"不要被仇恨支配自已😭"},{"pid":"3e83691397dd13f64eb08f783e29736a42841603","tid":1745775,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T11:38:48.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;但我只希望今日一個看似沒用的集會遊行，